<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Halaman Home</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- AOS CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden; /* Prevent horizontal scrolling */
        }
        .hero-section {
            background: url('/image/login.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
            height: 60vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .hero-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            z-index: -1;
        }
        .hero-section h1 {
            font-size: 5vw;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        .hero-section p {
            font-size: 2vw;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        .btn-login {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        .btn-login:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .welcome-text {
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .features {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .feature-item {
            flex: 1 1 30%;
            background: #1f1f1f;
            margin: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .feature-item:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        .feature-item i {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #007bff;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }
        footer a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-section h1 {
                font-size: 7vw;
            }
            .hero-section p {
                font-size: 3vw;
            }
            .features {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            .feature-item {
                flex: 1 1 80%;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .hero-section {
                height: 50vh;
            }
            .hero-section h1 {
                font-size: 8vw;
            }
            .hero-section p {
                font-size: 4vw;
            }
            .btn-login {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 12px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero-section">
        <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h1>Selamat Datang di Website Latihan-Login</h1>
            <p>Memberikan pengalaman login yang aman dan nyaman.</p>
            <a href="/login" class="btn-login">LOGIN <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i></a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="welcome-text" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2>Mengapa Memilih Kami?</h2>
            <p>Website ini dirancang untuk memberikan pengalaman login yang mudah, aman, dan cepat. Temukan berbagai fitur menarik kami!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature-item" data-aos="fade-right">
                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                <h3>Keamanan Tinggi</h3>
                <p>Data Anda dilindungi dengan enkripsi terbaru.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item" data-aos="fade-up">
                <i class="fas fa-user-friends"></i>
                <h3>Pengguna Ramah</h3>
                <p>Mudah digunakan oleh semua orang.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item" data-aos="fade-left">
                <i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i>
                <h3>Performa Cepat</h3>
                <p>Login dan akses halaman dengan cepat dan mudah.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Latihan-Login. Semua Hak Dilindungi. | <a href="/privacy">Kebijakan Privasi</a></p>
    </footer>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS and dependencies -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <!-- AOS JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.js"></script>
    <script>
        AOS.init();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
